cu.explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP '192.168.1.100' will cause wrong routing definitions, preventing DU from reaching CU and leading to F1 interface connection failure.

du.explanation_en: Modifying T1a_up timing parameters to [97, 197] introduces timing misalignment, causing inconsistent uplink timing that leads to synchronization issues and potential frame loss in the front-haul interface.
